  "detailed_description": "<i>Pay your debts. Escape hell. Or just buy another day.</i><br><br>Help Nathan beat an adrenaline-packed platformer as part of a tournament, to grab the prize and pay his debts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.poster.avif?t=1726948592\" width=382 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.webm?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.mp4?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A different narrative experience on top of an arcade/platformer gameplay.<br></li><li> 200+ Levels of frantic platforming.<br></li><li> Additional game modes for tons of replayability.<br></li><li> Simple controls and hybrid platformer-runner mechanics.<br></li><li> Original soundtrack (22 songs). </li></ul><br>The game includes an assist mode, which enables you to change overall difficulty, game speed and dash cooldown time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.poster.avif?t=1726948592\" width=630 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.webm?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.mp4?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/8f6df3935e8b06182917bb91b2262948.poster.avif?t=1726948592\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/8f6df3935e8b06182917bb91b2262948.webm?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/8f6df3935e8b06182917bb91b2262948.mp4?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Pay your debts. Escape hell. Or just buy another day.</i><br><br>Help Nathan beat an adrenaline-packed platformer as part of a tournament, to grab the prize and pay his debts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.poster.avif?t=1726948592\" width=382 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.webm?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/2e2ebcca619f83220944a1c3b1cacf44.mp4?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A different narrative experience on top of an arcade/platformer gameplay.<br></li><li> 200+ Levels of frantic platforming.<br></li><li> Additional game modes for tons of replayability.<br></li><li> Simple controls and hybrid platformer-runner mechanics.<br></li><li> Original soundtrack (22 songs). </li></ul><br>The game includes an assist mode, which enables you to change overall difficulty, game speed and dash cooldown time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.poster.avif?t=1726948592\" width=630 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.webm?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082000/extras/15e4bbb2fcc3ead7c9647fd2f575ef1d.mp4?t=1726948592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop plays